              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Site A: contact form immediately visible. Form submissions: 2.8% of visitors. Site B: portfolio first, contact form below. Form submissions: 4.3% of visitors. Build desire first, then capture. Forms above fold signal desperation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Headshot photos increase inquiry rates 28%</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Freelancer A: logo only. Inquiry rate: 3.9%. Freelancer B: professional headshot. Inquiry rate: 5.0%. Clients hire people, not brands. Face builds trust. Human connection matters.</p>
