      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-2"><strong>Creative Freelancers:</strong> Framer (9.5/10)</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-2"><strong>Consultants:</strong> Durable (CRM)</p>
